FuncDef: The display debugging mid_gne command displays enabled debugging functions for the MID_GNE module.
Examples: DCN packet debug switch is on
DCN event debug switch is on
DCN error debug switch is on
DCN process debug switch is on
ExtraInfo:
Usage Scenario
To check the enabled debugging functions for the MID_GNE module after a fault occurs on the DCN, run the display debugging mid_gne command. The command output facilitates fault locating.
Precautions
In VS mode, this command is supported only by the admin VS.
